Older than man.<br>
Older than dwarf.<br>
Only the great wurms remember our coming.<br>
<br>
But our failure is plain for all to see.<br>
We allowed our nature to seperate us,<br>
first Light from Dark and then Knowledge of Self from Knowledge of Earth.<br>
From one mighty and majestic race we have become three.<br>
<br>
And the others of the earth have taken what was ours.  Humans, dwarves, and gnomes worship our Gods and receive their favor.  Trolls wear the title of Shadow Knight while halfling Druids turn forest to farmland.<br>
<br>
We must unite, or we must surrender.  We must return to the ways of those who walked before us, or we will walk no more.<br>
<br>
We must rebuild the Nation of Elves. <br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
That about says it all.  This is to be an Elf only guild, High, Wood, and Dark all being equals.  It is to be a sort of neutral  ground for the Elvish races.  We do NOT intend to promote racism of any kind, but wish to unite a family too long apart, and make all others know we will not surrender our place in the world.<br>
<br>
If you are an elf and have some interest, please respond to this post.  If you are any other race and have comments or concerns feel free to post them, but you aren't the inteded audiance, so don't be offended if your points are not addressed.  Half Elves are an interesting concern, but at the moment the feeling is Half an Elf is NOT an Elf.<br>
<br>
Thanks for your time,<br>
<br>
Sywyn <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kelisk>Kelisk</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>No, YOU'RE evil<br>Look out! ...Rar!<br>New lizard Mod!</span><br>  Posts: 813<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/10/02 8:04:35 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm47.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=374.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.strike9.com/file.aspx/path=/CyrusVI/fullsize/keliskpic.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Elf only guild... testing the waters.</span><hr size=1> From an OOC perspective, best of luck to you. Sounds interesting, and I know how much dedication it can take from members and officers of such a guild to keep it going.  I hope you succeed! <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Kelisk Mae'Lokh</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">Chancellor of Skathris Ven'Sho--Patriarch of Cabilis</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=355953&quot;"><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Inspect Kelisk?</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=hollihawk>Hollihawk</A></s