<br>
I am not interested in having a large guild, 10 happy people are all I need, if it grows that's great, but I'd rather count on a good relatonship with other guilds when it comes to issues like raiding.<br>
<br>
As for RolePlay, I'll say that I would like to be an RP friendly group.  I would like the members to be considerate of Roleplayers, but I won't enforce roleplay by members.<br>
<br>
Also I know there have been other Good Elf groups, but I haven't seen any that included DE's.  Of course I know at this point in the game there are no more original ideas.  Except maybe for the one about the Gay Woodelves and the large Barbarian, Ogre and Troll woman who like to hang out with them.*<br>
