<br>
I think we're one of the very few such guilds Northern Elite (barbarians) and Kerran Untity (Vah Shir) are some of the other few.<br>
<br>
It's definitely tough to keep the theme.  You will inevitably meet fellow adventurers who you will form bonds with who can't enter your guild, and that gets hard.  Forming alliances with other strongly themed guilds helps.  Overall, I've always felt it promoted the RP nature of the server.<br>
<br>
You might actually make it even tougher on yourselves to have all elves.  Most like the split, but it could be an interesting theme in itself. <p><A HREF="http://eq.guildmagic.com/character.cfm?ID=169421">Trevian</A><br>
